    <data key="d0">Zigbang: A Hybrid API of Serverless and ECS, Infra as a Code via CDK</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0F7KDLz-kIQ</data>
    <data key="d2">Hybrid architecture combining ECS/Fargate for steady-state workloads and API Gateway/Lambda to handle sudden traffic spikes. Implements dynamic DNS weighted routing via an AWS SDK monitoring loop.</data>
    <data key="d3">compute_intensive,interactive,control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
